  "description": "Automated SEO Audit in n8n – Your All-in-One Website Optimization Tool!\n\nLooking for a powerful, fully automated solution to analyze your website’s SEO? Our custom n8n workflow is designed just for you!\n\nWhat does this workflow do?\nOur advanced SEO audit collects all the essential data that impact your site’s search engine rankings, including:\n\nAnalysis of meta tags (title, description) with actionable optimization recommendations\n\nVerification of H1 and H2 headings, presented in clear, organized tables\n\nChecking internal, external, and broken links for full link health insights\n\nDetection of key technical files: robots.txt and sitemap.xml\n\nIdentification of Google Analytics and social media links implementation\n\nEvaluation of URL friendliness and mobile responsiveness\n\nSSL certificate and noindex meta tag presence checks\n\nIntegration with Google PageSpeed API for website speed and performance metrics\n\nDeepSeek API support for in-depth content and keyword analysis\n\nGeneration of clean, user-friendly HTML reports ready to share with clients or teams\n\nWhy choose this workflow?\nEasy integration – just connect your Google PageSpeed and DeepSeek API keys, and the workflow automatically gathers and analyzes all data.\n\nFully automated – run the workflow and get a comprehensive SEO report with zero manual work.\n\nScalable – audit single pages or entire website portfolios effortlessly.\n\nCustomizable – pre-built functions and templates ready for extension or integration with your systems.\n\nProfessional HTML report – visually appealing and packed with actionable insights for your team or clients.\n\nHow to get started?\nSet up your Google PageSpeed and DeepSeek API keys.\n\nConnect them within n8n – no extra steps needed!\n\nRun the workflow and receive a detailed SEO audit report that will help you improve rankings and boost traffic.\n\nAutomate your SEO audits with n8n – faster, easier, and more effective than ever before!\n\nI recorded video:\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=solB17pXYbc\n\n\nIf you want, I can also prepare a shorter marketing snippet or social media posts. Just let me know: jacobmarketingservice@gmail.com\n\n",
